// Blueprint Class: BP_BaseHumanCharacter
// Parent Class: Character
// Description: Base class for all human characters in the prehistoric world

/*
BLUEPRINT CONFIGURATION:

Components:
- Mesh (SkeletalMeshComponent): MetaHuman base mesh
- CharacterAppearance (UCharacterAppearanceComponent): Custom appearance system
- CapsuleComponent: Collision (Height: 192, Radius: 42)

Default Values:
- Use Controller Rotation Yaw: false
- Orient Rotation to Movement: true
- Rotation Rate: (Yaw=540.0)
- Max Walk Speed: 400.0
- Jump Z Velocity: 600.0

MetaHuman Setup:
- Skeletal Mesh: /Game/MetaHumans/Common/Male/Medium/NormalWeight/Body/m_med_nrw_body
- Animation Blueprint: ABP_Manny (retargeted for MetaHuman)
- Physics Asset: MetaHuman default physics

Material Slots:
0. M_MetaHuman_Body (skin material)
1. M_MetaHuman_Face (face material) 
2. M_MetaHuman_Eye (eye material)
3. M_MetaHuman_Hair (hair material)
4. M_TribalClothing_Base (clothing material)

Variables:
- CharacterData (FCharacterData): Current character configuration
- bIsProtagonist (bool): Whether this is the player character
- TribalGroup (ETribalGroup): Which tribe this character belongs to
- UniqueIdentifier (FString): Unique ID for save/load system

Functions:
- InitializeCharacter(CharacterData): Setup character from data
- ApplyTribalClothing(TribalGroup): Apply appropriate clothing
- GetCharacterBiography(): Return character's backstory
- IsRecognizedBy(OtherCharacter): Check if characters know each other

Events:
- BeginPlay: Initialize appearance system
- OnInteracted: Handle player interaction
- OnSpoken: Handle dialogue initiation
*/

